ports.behavior:
forward customer_name_from_manager
assign DataOrigin.Asia if TRUE from customers
assign DataOrigin.USA if TRUE from customers
assign DataStatus.Regular if TRUE from customers
assign DataStatus.Celebrity if TRUE from customers

forward customer_name_from_clerk
assign DataOrigin.Asia if DataOrigin.Asia from customer_name_from_clerk,customers
assign DataOrigin.USA if DataOrigin.USA from customer_name_from_clerk,customers
assign DataStatus.Regular if DataStatus.Regular from customer_name_from_clerk,customers
assign DataStatus.Celebrity if DataStatus.Celebrity from customer_name_from_clerk,customers

forward customer_name
forward customers
assign DataOrigin.Asia if DataOrigin.Asia from customer_name
assign DataOrigin.USA if DataOrigin.USA from customer_name
assign DataStatus.Regular if DataStatus.Regular from customer_name
assign DataStatus.Celebrity if DataStatus.Celebrity from customers

forward customer_name
forward customers
assign DataOrigin.Asia if DataOrigin.Asia from customer_name
assign DataOrigin.USA if DataOrigin.USA from customer_name
assign DataStatus.Regular if DataStatus.Regular from customer_name
assign DataStatus.Celebrity if DataStatus.Celebrity from customers

forward customer
forward customer_name
assign DataOrigin.Asia if DataOrigin.USA from customer,customer_name
